msgid ""
msgstr ""
"Project-Id-Version: Yakuza 6 Translation\n"
"Last-Translator: SavT\n"
"MIME-Version: 1.0\n"
"Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8\n"
"Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit\n"
"Language: it\n"

msgctxt "0||||4"
msgid "That's enough of this!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1||||4"
msgid "I'm sorry. I just..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2||||4"
msgid "You'll never amount to anything with that attitude.\r\nDon't you understand?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3||||4"
msgid "I-I do. I just wanted to see\r\nhim one last time before I left."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5||||4"
msgid "How are you ever going to survive in Tokyo like this?\r\nIt's a harsh world up there."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||||4"
msgid "Idol life isn't all just fun and games!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "7||||4"
msgid "So, that girl wants to be an idol?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "8||||4"
msgid "B-But..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "9||||4"
msgid "If you're serious about pursuing this career path,\r\nyou'll need to leave this town, and him, behind."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "10||||4"
msgid "Idols aren't allowed to be in love."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "12||||4"
msgid "I suggest you heed my warning."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "13||||4"
msgid "Hey, are you okay?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "15||||4"
msgid "You're trying to become an idol, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "16||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17||||4"
msgid "Sorry, I didn't mean to eavesdrop on you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "18||||4"
msgid "I'm such a disgrace, aren't I?\r\nI shouldn't be crying in public like this..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "19||||4"
msgid "......"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "20||||4"
msgid "Cheer up, kid. I'll see you around."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "22||||4"
msgid "No, I really appreciate the offer.\r\n I think it'll help talking to someone."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "23||||4"
msgid "Hey, are you okay?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||||4"
msgid "Why don't you talk to me for a bit?\r\nIt'll be better for you than crying here all alone."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "26||||4"
msgid "I don't want to force you, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||||4"
msgid "My name is Misa."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "29||||4"
msgid "You're from Tokyo, right, Kiryu-san?\r\nI didn't think you'd be so... kind."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "30||||4"
msgid "Anyone would be worried about\r\na girl your age crying in the street."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "31||||4"
msgid "Anyway, feel free to tell me what's bothering you.\r\nThat was some argument you were having."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "32||||4"
msgid "That woman from earlier is from a production firm\r\nbased up in Tokyo. She's my manager, Endo-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "33||||4"
msgid "Endo seemed really upset with you for some reason."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "34||||4"
msgid "Yeah, there's a pretty big rule I'm breaking...\r\nOnce you become an idol, dating's off-limits."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "35||||4"
msgid "That's why she was yelling at me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "36||||4"
msgid "Off-limits, huh..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "37||||4"
msgid "What happened is, I had finally had a breakout\r\nmoment in an audition, and got reassigned to Tokyo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "38||||4"
msgid "But, that's when I realized something: I have feelings\r\nfor an old childhood friend and senpai of mine."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "39||||4"
msgid "Even though I was taking lessons about being an idol,\r\nthe thought of leaving him worried me to no end."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "40||||4"
msgid "That's understandable."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||||4"
msgid "He's been so supportive about me realizing my\r\ndream, though. He was there when nobody else was."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "42||||4"
msgid "Now that I think about it, he was the first person\r\nI told about me moving to Tokyo after the audition, too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "44||||4"
msgid "Even when my parents and the other adults refused\r\nto support me, he was there, cheering me on."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||||4"
msgid "Sounds pretty special."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||||4"
msgid "He is. That's why I want to make sure he knows\r\nhow I feel before I leave for Tokyo forever."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "47||||4"
msgid "If he accepts me... I think I'm going to stay here.\r\nI won't know his answer until I tell him, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "48||||4"
msgid "I guess it's no surprise your manager is upset."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "49||||4"
msgid "Honestly, I know it's dumb."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||||4"
msgid "This is supposed to be my make-or-break moment\r\nas an idol, but my stupid emotions are in the way..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "51||||4"
msgid "Maybe... Maybe I should just go to Tokyo.\r\nCan I really ignore my feelings like that...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "52||||4"
msgid "No matter what, you should go tell him how you feel.\r\nAt least that's what I would do."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "53||||4"
msgid "Really?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "54||||4"
msgid "If you don't, you'll always wonder what would\r\nhave happened if you hadn't run away."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||||4"
msgid "That's how it goes."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "56||||4"
msgid "Oh. I hadn't thought of it like that..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||||4"
msgid "It's better if you don't go see him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "58||||4"
msgid "If you give up on your idol dream now,\r\nall the support he gave you will have been for nothing."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "59||||4"
msgid "But if I go to Tokyo now, who knows if\r\nI'll ever be able to see him again..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||||4"
msgid "You can either become an idol, or stay\r\nwith this guy. The choice is yours."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||||4"
msgid "I-I guess you're right about that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||||4"
msgid "Why don't I help you forget about him?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||||4"
msgid "A rebound is always a quick fix for a broken heart.\r\nOlder men tend to be more experienced, too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||||4"
msgid "Um... You can't be serious."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||||4"
msgid "I thought you were nice for listening to me,\r\nbut now your real intentions come to light."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "67||||4"
msgid "......"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "68||||4"
msgid "......"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "69||||4"
msgid "It was a joke."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "70||||4"
msgid "Oh, good! Funny joke, huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "71||||4"
msgid "...Yeah."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "72||||4"
msgid "......"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "73||||4"
msgid "Anyway, what are you going to do?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "74||||4"
msgid "Um, I think I'm going to go see him.\r\nI can't leave for Tokyo without saying how I feel."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "75||||4"
msgid "Right. I can't say I'm surprised."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "76||||4"
msgid "When people are troubled by something, they usually\r\njust need to look for the answer within themselves."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "77||||4"
msgid "Oh. So that's why you decided to talk to me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "78||||4"
msgid "Thank you, Kiryu-san. I feel a little bit\r\nbetter now that I've talked to you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "79||||4"
msgid "It was nothing. Well, I should be going.\r\nAre you going to be okay?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "80||||4"
msgid "Yes!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||||4"
msgid "What's going on, Misa? Aren't you going\r\nto tell that senpai of yours how you feel?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "82||||4"
msgid "I tried, but I got kinda nervous...\r\nSorry, but can you give me some more time?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "83||||4"
msgid "Sure. I wasn't trying to rush you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "84||||4"
msgid "Hm? Is that... Misa? So the guy\r\nmust be the one she mentioned earlier."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "85||||4"
msgid "Um, well, there's something\r\nI really need to talk to you about!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "86||||4"
msgid "What's going on, Misa? I'm all ears."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "87||||4"
msgid "Um, do you remember how I told you my dream\r\nof becoming an idol back in middle school, senpai?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "88||||4"
msgid "Yeah, of course I do."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "89||||4"
msgid "It was after you saw Haruka Sawamura's\r\nlast concert on TV. That was what inspired you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "90||||4"
msgid "So Misa wants to be an idol now\r\nbecause of Haruka...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "91||||4"
msgid "Back then, everyone made fun of me and\r\ncalled me names. You were different, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "92||||4"
msgid "You've supported me nonstop since then."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||||4"
msgid "The truth is, um... from that day forward, I..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "95||||4"
msgid "It would be rude of me to keep listening to this.\r\nI should get out of here before they notice me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "96||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "97||||4"
msgid "Well, well! Look what we got here!\r\nY'guys're real cute, y'know?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "98||||4"
msgid "This ain't no place t'be gettin'\r\nall lovey-dovey like that, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||||4"
msgid "U-Uh, excuse me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "100||||4"
msgid "Hey, we're in the middle of something! Go away!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "101||||4"
msgid "Y'really got the balls t'be tellin' us off?\r\nDon't y'know yer in a public place? Huh!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "102||||4"
msgid "It looks like I might need to get involved."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "103||||4"
msgid "Hey bro, we don't got business with ya.\r\nWe're way more into this li'l lady over here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "104||||4"
msgid "'At's right! Yer in our way, brat! Y'better get\r\nlost before we gotta lay the beatdown on ya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||||4"
msgid "Okay! Please don't hurt me...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "106||||4"
msgid "Huh? S-Senpai?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "107||||4"
msgid "(Some senpai he is.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "108||||4"
msgid "Look, Misa. These guys probably aren't so bad, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "109||||4"
msgid "Plus, I've got entrance exams coming up.\r\nI can't be getting hurt now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "110||||4"
msgid "W-Wait, what...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "111||||4"
msgid "I'm really sorry!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "112||||4"
msgid "Senpai! Please, don't leave me!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "113||||4"
msgid "Jus' forget about him, li'l lady.\r\nYer boyfriend abandoned ya here, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "114||||4"
msgid "How 'bout y'have some fun with us instead?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||||4"
msgid "I said, no! You guys are\r\nnothing but a bunch of thugs!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "116||||4"
msgid "Huh? What're y'lookin' at, gramps?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "117||||4"
msgid "This ain't any o' yer business!\r\nGet lost, ya old fuck!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "118||||4"
msgid "This actually isn't any of <font_kind=yakuza_italic>your</font_kind> business.\r\nYou interrupted a tender moment here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "119||||4"
msgid "If you want to lay your hands on the girl,\r\nyou're going to have to go through me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "120||||4"
msgid "Who the hell's this shit?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "121||||4"
msgid "Ugh, whatever. We're gonna make ya\r\nregret gettin' in our way! C'mon!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "122||||4"
msgid "H-Hold on a sec, old man! Look,\r\nwe're only doin' this 'cause someone asked us!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "123||||4"
msgid "I think that's enough.\r\nYou've served your purpose."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "124||||4"
msgid "Endo-san? Wait, what's going on?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "125||||4"
msgid "That woman... She's Misa's manager, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "126||||4"
msgid "I'm the one who hired these men. I wanted\r\nto test how devoted your senpai is to you, Misa."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "127||||4"
msgid "What...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "128||||4"
msgid "As I expected, he instead showed us the true cowardice\r\nin his heart. Has that cured your lovesickness, Misa?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "129||||4"
msgid "Endo-san..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "130||||4"
msgid "I haven't actually started packing for Tokyo yet.\r\nI should probably go do that, huh..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "131||||4"
msgid "Yes. It's for the best."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "133||||4"
msgid "Misa!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "134||||4"
msgid "You've done quite enough already... Kazuma Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "135||||4"
msgid "What? You know who I am?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "136||||4"
msgid "Of course I do."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||||4"
msgid "Everyone in the industry knows that face of yours.\r\nYou're the yakuza who forced Haruka into retirement."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "138||||4"
msgid "I don't care why you're down here in Onomichi,\r\nbut I need you to stop trying to help Misa."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "139||||4"
msgid "Her conscience needs to be clear when she\r\nheads up to Tokyo. Isn't that right, senpai?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "140||||4"
msgid "What? I don't get it. You were in on this scheme, too?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||||4"
msgid "Yes. I'm actually the one who came up\r\nwith the idea to begin with."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||||4"
msgid "Those other guys are classmates of mine.\r\nAll Endo-san did was agree to follow along."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "143||||4"
msgid "Man, y'really put us through the ringer."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "144||||4"
msgid "Sorry about that, you guys. I'll buy you\r\ndinner to make up for it, okay?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "145||||4"
msgid "Sure, sure. See ya later."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "146||||4"
msgid "Care to explain what's going on here?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "147||||4"
msgid "I don't know if this is much of an explanation,\r\nbut I've been there for Misa every step of the way."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "148||||4"
msgid "I know just how hard she's had to work\r\nto get to where she is today."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "149||||4"
msgid "That's why... That's why she needs to focus on\r\nbeing an idol instead of confessing to a chump like me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "150||||4"
msgid "He's had feelings for Misa for many years now.\r\nSince far before she realized how she felt."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "151||||4"
msgid "So this was all for Misa, then.\r\nThat's why you're pulling yourself away from her."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "152||||4"
msgid "If I stop her from pursuing her dream of stardom,\r\nI'd never be able to forgive myself."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "153||||4"
msgid "Even if Misa and I ended up together,\r\nI'm sure that would always weigh heavy on my mind."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "155||||4"
msgid "You know, when Endo-san told me the other day how\r\nMisa felt about me, I was honestly over the moon."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "156||||4"
msgid "But that's exactly why I didn't think I'd be able to trick\r\nher like this. I can't stand the thought of hurting her."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "157||||4"
msgid "So this was all for her sake..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "158||||4"
msgid "If Misa abandons her feelings for me, she'll be able to\r\npush onward toward her dream without any regrets."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "159||||4"
msgid "Honestly, I don't care how she thinks of me now.\r\nI'd do whatever it takes for her."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "161||||4"
msgid "Even for someone you love,\r\nthat's not an easy path to walk."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "162||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san, was it?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "163||||4"
msgid "If you ever see Misa around town,\r\ncould you not tell her about this?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "164||||4"
msgid "To be perfectly honest, I'd much rather\r\nlet her know what's going on."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "165||||4"
msgid "But I'm just an outsider. It's not\r\nreally my place to say anything."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "166||||4"
msgid "Thank you so much. Goodbye, then."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "167||||4"
msgid "I appreciate this, Kiryu-san.\r\nLet me show my gratitude."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "168||||4"
msgid "Is this supposed to keep me quiet?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "169||||4"
msgid "It's a simple thank-you gift."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "170||||4"
msgid "You know, even though you're a famous yakuza,\r\nyou actually turned out to be quite understanding."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "171||||4"
msgid "Huh. You're kinder than you look, too.\r\nAnyway, take good care of Misa."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "172||||4"
msgid "I will."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "173||||4"
msgid "Speaking of which, where did Misa run off to?\r\nShe seemed pretty shocked earlier."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "174||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "175||||4"
msgid "Misa? How long have you been there?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "176||||4"
msgid "Wait!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "177||||4"
msgid "I... I didn't hear anything, promise!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "178||||4"
msgid "Then why did you run away?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "179||||4"
msgid "......"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "180||||4"
msgid "I know you're probably confused after hearing all that.\r\nI'm sure it's hard to know everyone is deceiving you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "181||||4"
msgid "But I need you to listen."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "182||||4"
msgid "Pretend like you didn't hear any of that. Go to Tokyo,\r\nand succeed. That's what Endo and your senpai want."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "183||||4"
msgid "So you're taking their side, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "184||||4"
msgid "I guess I am."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "185||||4"
msgid "You should be a track star instead of an idol.\r\nIt's damn impressive how fast you can run."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "186||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "187||||4"
msgid "Plus if you did that, there wouldn't be\r\nany problem with you dating your senpai."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "188||||4"
msgid "That's a dumb joke..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "190||||4"
msgid "Love is more important than entertainment."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "191||||4"
msgid "That senpai you admire so much is a great guy.\r\nPeople aren't really like that up in Tokyo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "192||||4"
msgid "But if I stay here, do you think he'll really be happy?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "193||||4"
msgid "......"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "194||||4"
msgid "You heard what he was saying earlier, Kiryu-san.\r\nHe'd regret holding me back from my dream."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "195||||4"
msgid "If I want to keep him happy and in love with me,\r\nleaving for Tokyo is my only option."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "196||||4"
msgid "You may be right."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "197||||4"
msgid "Hey, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "198||||4"
msgid "What is it?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "199||||4"
msgid "Well, I never would have fallen for senpai if he was the\r\nkind of guy who'd abandon me to some random thugs."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "201||||4"
msgid "I saw right through him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "202||||4"
msgid "I knew something was up, so I pretended\r\nto run off and hid nearby to watch."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "203||||4"
msgid "After all, idols have to be good at acting, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "204||||4"
msgid "I'm so happy, though. I had no idea he was\r\nso invested in making sure I achieved my dreams."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "205||||4"
msgid "I... I won't let him down.\r\nI'm going to give this all I've got."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "206||||4"
msgid "Good. I'm sure your senpai will be happy to hear that.\r\nHe should be able to keep his distance in peace."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "207||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "208||||4"
msgid "Idols aren't allowed to be in love, remember?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "209||||4"
msgid "Um... do you think he'll still be waiting for me\r\nwhen I'm done with everything I want to do?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "210||||4"
msgid "Him? He'd wait even if you told him not to."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "211||||4"
msgid "I hope you're right."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "212||||4"
msgid "Well, good luck, Misa. I'll be rooting for you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "214||||4"
msgid "Um, Kiryu-san..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "215||||4"
msgid "Becoming an idol's only the first part of my dream."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "216||||4"
msgid "To be honest, there's one more thing I want\r\nto do in the entertainment industry."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "217||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "218||||4"
msgid "I want to perform in a crowded dome full of\r\nloving fans. That's where I'll announce my retirement."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "219||||4"
msgid "Everyone in the audience and watching on TV will be\r\nso surprised. I'll run off the stage, and be gone forever."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "220||||4"
msgid "Just like Haruka-chan."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "221||||4"
msgid "I hope you're joking."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "222||||4"
msgid "So, what do you think? You have firsthand\r\nexperience with that, right, Kiryu-san?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "223||||4"
msgid "Don't do it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "224||||4"
msgid "It'll be nothing but trouble for those around you.\r\nThe media seriously never lets up..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "225||||4"
msgid "It's a harsh world out there, huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "226||||4"
msgid "Yeah."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "227||||4"
msgid "I'll have to do my best."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "228||||4"
msgid "Um... Kiryu-san, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "229||||4"
msgid "Hm? Oh, you're the guy Misa is in love with."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "230||||4"
msgid "Yeah. I want to thank you\r\nfor everything you did for her."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "231||||4"
msgid "Have you spoken to her since then?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "232||||4"
msgid "I haven't. She already knows how I feel,\r\nand I already know how she feels about me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "233||||4"
msgid "Someday soon she'll be on TV and in magazines.\r\nI can't wait to see what she makes of herself."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "234||||4"
msgid "Right."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "235||||4"
msgid "Though... even though I'm trying to act cool,\r\nI can't help but wonder if I made the right decision."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "236||||4"
msgid "I wouldn't have time to worry if I was still\r\nwith the team, but I already retired."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "237||||4"
msgid "Uh-huh. What kind of team were you on?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "238||||4"
msgid "Baseball. The team wasn't the greatest around,\r\nbut I was the captain for a few years."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "239||||4"
msgid "Oh? I'm actually on a baseball team myself.\r\nIt's just a little local one, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "240||||4"
msgid "If you'd like, maybe you could come play\r\non our team between classes sometime."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "241||||4"
msgid "Are you sure?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "242||||4"
msgid "It'll help you stop worrying so much. Besides,\r\nanyone with experience is welcome on our team."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "243||||4"
